  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing emergency support to people affected by the conflict in Ukraine. Currently working with partners in Poland and Romania to support refugees with the following activities: 
kits to HH in 5 provinces 
- Multipurpose cash distributions to 4,400 individuals in Poland
- Protection activities - support to GBV survivors and establishing hotlines 
- Anti-trafficking activities in Romania
- Providing essential supplies and information to refugees at border crossing points in Poland and Romania</narrative>
